 />\n2）你都確定唔到係咪真貨 萬一二手罩...<br />\n3）你出去買/交收就要曝露係人多嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n無錯 我就係情願麻煩多十倍都唔會益無良商家<br />\n簡單啲嚟講 我射落海都唔會益你<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係決定食炒價 唔好相信任何<br />\n「預定」、「嚟緊香港」、「入訂金先」<br />\n<br />\n一定要面交 一手交錢一手交貨"},{"pid":"51abdc6e44d9b55b36223c3a74a1aa173c578e67","tid":1865120,"uid":28720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3509e4ea3b747cfd9c46ce8d5b37abeaa5bc168e","tid":1865120,"uid":35031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c89b07e9bedc881d177fb19729f7c26df757083a","tid":1865120,"uid":28720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAOgssU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAOgssU.png&h=53a64612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣係咪上咗機。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:58:07.000Z","msg":"到左<br />\n等香港郵政派...<br />\n但香港郵政唔係跟EMS到港日決定先後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8579854ac0061d7bc032108dd8aba925271476ee","tid":1865120,"uid":28720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4c899cc13fe14cb214634bbb1ee5bd1f9ab3830","tid":1865120,"uid":129321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c89b07e9bedc881d177fb19729f7c26df757083a","tid":1865120,"uid":28720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAOgssU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAOgssU.png&h=53a64612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣係咪上咗機。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"啊鬼你都係轉返英文喇..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfee8c7a4165c19f1d26a33dd8072392f798dad7","tid":1865120,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:29:32.000Z","msg":"28號到依家仲喺 琦玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg