買/交收就要曝露係人多嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n無錯 我就係情願麻煩多十倍都唔會益無良商家<br />\n簡單啲嚟講 我射落海都唔會益你<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係決定食炒價 唔好相信任何<br />\n「預定」、「嚟緊香港」、「入訂金先」<br />\n<br />\n一定要面交 一手交錢一手交貨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"Dhl咁快? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a191d0407465aec4d508e216848c8abf7bbb126","tid":1865120,"uid":23575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"834263b887602a31c3352cc819354e8396be8863","tid":1865120,"uid":275845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UYTuCX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UYTuCX.png&h=96f5a45d&s={SIZE}\" />已經幾日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:04:00.000Z","msg":"我都係咁"}]}